CATALOGUE, 2020
</bibRefCitation>
), at an elevation of 
<quantity box="[1206,1316,1558,1583]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.43" metricValueMax="2.36" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="5" pageNumber="208" unit="m" value="143.0" valueMax="236.0" valueMin="50.0">
50– 
